&lt;h1 id="prerequisite">Prerequisite&lt;/h1>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a class="sources-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/installing/" >Install hugo&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a class="sources-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/quick-start/" >Make your site&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Minimum version of hugo 0.74.0 .&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="install-theme">Install theme&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>When your website is on. You will install the theme.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Go in the folder /themes/ and run the command :&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="by-clone">by clone&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">
git clone https://github.com/subversive-eu/hugo-subversive.git
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>To update the theme use this :&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">
cd themes/hugo-PaperMod
git pull
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="by-submodule">by submodule&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">
git submodule add https://github.com/subversive-eu/hugo-subversive.git hugo-subversive
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>To update the theme use this :&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">
git submodule update --remote --merge
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="by-download">by download&lt;/h2>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>On github repository, clic on -code (green button) then download zip.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Copy and paste the folder in your sitefolder/themes/ rename it by hugo-subversive.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>To understand the file configuration checkout, and take attention of &lt;a class="sources-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/subversive-eu/hugo-subversive/tree/exampleSite" >exampleSite&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="configyml">config.yml&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="theme">theme&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>In your config file write the name of your folder like this :&lt;/p>
&lt;p>config.yml :&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>theme: hugo-subversive&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>config.toml :&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>theme = &amp;quot;hugo-subversive&amp;quot;&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
